      "content": "Mixing even a small amount of wine with diazepam is not a safe way to encourage sleep; it's a gamble with your system. The alcohol will interact unpredictably with the medication, potentially causing you to become overly sedated or experience adverse reactions. To ensure you fall asleep safely, wait until your body processes what you already consumed before taking your medication. If you're still wired, consider taking a warm bath before bed instead of mixing substances.",
