      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you, but i've read online that in very low amounts it actually works as a synergist to help with anxiety and falling asleep. like, most people do it for relaxation. if i just take half a pill and have a few sips, it shouldn't be a big deal right? i really just need to know if it's actually \"dangerous\" or if you're just being overly cautious. it feels like a lot of effort to wait hours when i'm this tired.",
