      "content": "Online anecdotes are not medical advice, and the synergistic effect you read about is a dangerous misunderstanding of pharmacology. Even small amounts can cause unpredictable sedation, respiratory depression, or worse when combined with a benzodiazepine like diazepam. Instead of risking your safety, try taking your prescribed dose with a glass of sparkling water to help it absorb smoothly. If you are truly exhausted, focus on deep, slow breathing exercises to calm your nervous system right now.",
